title: Miniature gingerbread house kit on a board for dollhouse in 1:12 scale
description: A miniature gingerbread house kit on cardboard is a unique and charming addition to any dollhouse or miniature collection. Each element is meticulously handcrafted and painted by me, ensuring exceptional detail and authenticity. All pieces are securely glued to the cardboard, and this one-of-a-kind set will never be replicated, making it a truly special item for collectors.
